To Install
==========

1) Download the zip file (FoxNewsLive.zip) from the link above.

2) Extract the contents (directory plugin.video.fox.news.live) to the XBMC addons directory
    Windows: C:\Users\[JohnDoe]\AppData\Roaming\XBMC\addons
    Linux: ~/.xbmc/addons

3) Restart XBMC.

4) Go to Video add-ons and you should see Fox News Live.